-- EU Says `No Plan' Being Readied for Spain, Calling Reports `Speculation'
-- Kevin Costelloe
-- 2010-06-14T07:09:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/eu-says-no-plan-being-readied-for-spain-calling-reports-speculation-.html

          
          
             The European Commission said today
that there is no financial aid plan being prepared for Spain.
“There is no plan being prepared for Spain,” European
Commission spokesman Amadeu Altafaj said by telephone. He called
news media reports that a plan is being prepared “mere
speculation.”  
          
          


  


        